<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.9.4">
<l>koṇṭalvaṇ ṇāviṅkē pōta rāyē</l>
<l rend="indent">kōyiṟpiḷ ḷāyiṅkē pōta rāyē</l>
<l>teṇtirai cūḻtirup pērkki ṭanta</l>
<l rend="indent">tirunāra ṇāviṅkē pōta rāyē</l>
<l>uṇṭuvan tēṉamma meṉṟu colli</l>
<l rend="indent">ōṭi yakampuka vāycci tāṉum</l>
<l>kaṇṭeti rēceṉ ṟeṭuttuk koḷḷak</l>
<l rend="indent">kaṇṇapi rāṉkaṟṟa kalvi tāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Cloud- coloured One, come here!</l>
<l rend="indent">Child of the temple, come here!</l>
<l>Divine Nāraṇā who lay in Tiruppēr,</l>
<l rend="indent">surrounded by clear waves, come here!</l>
<l>When [he] ran inside saying</l>
<l rend="indent">“I have [already] eaten food,”</l>
<l>the herdess, seeing him, goes and lifts [him up],</l>
<l>this is the lesson learned by Kaṇṇapirāṉ!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
